Fuck it...I think im finally done.

~TwEeK~

Well...the search for a job is finally over for the time being.  I got a job at rockwell farms...a greenhouse.  It sucks and I hurt when I get off of work and when I get up in the mornings and a fucking day really.  But I have Saturdays and Sundays of...maybe Mondays...I dont know.  Well...just thought I will let people know that I wont be doing anything during the week...so if you want me you have to wait until Friday night...except Bif and Aura...their the only friends I have in this town...so...yea.

~TwEeK~

Lately I have been looking for a job.  The search is going no where at all, some people seem to think that im not trying at all to find one, but GODDAMNIT I AM.  Its not fucking easy to find a job in this shit hole town.

But anyways...

I got drunk the other night for the first time in awhile off of some Jack Daniels (mmmmmmm Jack Daniels).  Actually I was more then drunk...I was all out fucking up.  Damn I miss getting that fucked up sometimes.

-OuT-
~TwEeK~

Im on the brink of fucking destruction right now.  Im tired of all the time arguing, being lied to, accused of trying to start arguments, im tired of it ...all of it.

I love Christina to death and dont want to lose her...but if shit keeps going the way it is right now...its going to happen and im going to be the one hurting feelings.

On another note...besides all that bullshit...everything has been fine...hanging out with Bif and Aura (yes they are the only 2 friends I have near where I live...sad...isnt it).  Been hangin out at there house doing the reefer, playing video games listening to music, you know, shit you do when you go to Bifs house.

Well...nothing more to say.

-OuT-
~TwEeK~

Why is it so fucking hard to find a job in Rowan county.  This place fucking sucks...im on the fucking edge and want to get out of here.  To a town where no one fucking knows me and I dont know any of them.  Is that so fucking bad to ask for...a job and out of this shit hole.  If it wasnt for Bif and Aura I probaly would have already killed myself out of bordom...lol.  But serioulsy...how is it possible for one town to be so shitty???  I feel sorry for the person who has no friends in a town like this.

-OuT-
~TwEeK~

Well...the 2nd worst thing happend.  Christina moved to Troy.  We are still together and all that...she just went to live there with her mom because she has 2 job offers there.  So im looking for a job and when I get it im going to save to get my tag and insurance on my car then im going to get me and Christina a place so we can live together.  

I have a question to ask everyone...and please answer if you can.  

Why does love hurt so fucking much???

Can anyone answer me that...I love Christina so fucking much...I cant even begin to explain the love I have for her.  But this shit that shes doing is for the best.

-OuT-
~TwEeK~

Im sitting here waiting patiently for Christinas return...in the meen time I will be bored out of my fucking skull.  But its all good...tonight is going to be a good night ;)...

But anyway...if anyone wants to do anything today...give me a call...I will be here alone until about 6 or so...maybe sooner...maybe later...I dont know.

-OuT-

~TwEeK~

Yea...iv been distant lately to all my friends and I appologize.  Its just ;ate;y I havnt been feeling well at all (thats what I get for smoking Newports).  But anyway...sihk-or treat is coming up and I cant fucking wait.  Its going to be fucking awsome.

Anyway...I finaly got my GED so the party shall commence soon...hehehe >:)

Well...I have nothing more to say...

Later
~TwEeK~

Well...all I have really done is hang out with Bif and Aura alot lately.  I did hang out with Bryan a day this week...we got drunk and i got high and drunk...then he went to some chicks house.  I havnt seen Bif or Aura in a couple days...im going to try and hang out with them today.  

Also it seems that I might get back with Christina...I dont know why...but I do care about her though...and yea, I already know im going to get bitched out by alot of people so just bring it on and I will listen and it could possibly change my mind.  Just dont be too mean...please.

Later
~TwEeK~

You are the bad boy / girl of your school. You
have little faith in yourself and usually find
escape in some sort of addicting substance or
yourself. You would rather torture others
above anything else. You regularly skip
school and when you go, always tend to ditch a
certain class. Some classmates can fear you
while others pity you...and your family. (No
offense) Your cruel behavior and abject
personality tends to single you out from the
crowd...and you prefer life this way at times.
However, lonliness can rear its ugly head and
force you seek a way to silence it. But be
warned, your path is dangerous... but only a
strong person can walk this road.

Some
ideal occupations for you can be a Police
officer, Celebrity (who doesn't love the
badasses?), Wrestler, Polotician, or some sort
of leader. Either way, your destined to be
known by many.

What type of teenager are you?
brought to you by Quizilla
In your eyes, people can't seem to see anything
because your eyes are covered up by tears! You
are constantly hurt and depressed... No one
seems to understand how you feel because
everyone is scared to get close to you... You
long to be able to reach out and tell someone
everything, and all of your problems... But you
have no one to tell, or they just don't seem to
want to hear what you have to say. You've been
hurt many times that you don't seem to have any
tears left to shed, or if you do, they're an
endless river flowing... You've started to hide
and bottle up all or your problems and
feelings, hoping that maybe they just will go
away... You want company, but at the same time,
you're scared of it. Your sanctuary is your
room where you can just be alone and try to
throw away all of your aching pains. You're
dark and mysterious and people like you for
that reason. Even if you think you're all by
yourself in the dark, someone is always there
with you. Your special someone wants to admit
and show their feelings towards you, but
they're afraid of how you'll take it. Get out
more and enjoy life because, it is far too long
to frown your way through :)

Well...nothing else has really happend to me in the last couple days...so im going to go for now...

This is what I just found out...

Korn has parted ways with guitarist Brian Head Welch, who has chosen the Lord Jesus Christ as his savior, and will be dedicating his musical pursuits to that end.  Korn respects Brian's wishes and hopes he finds the happiness he is searching for.  Jonathan, Fieldy, James and David are personally closer than ever, and are currently in the studio working on their 8th record, the follow up to their highly successful Greatest Hits Album.  The record is due to be released this coming September.

I am in shock...I dont even know what to think.  But they have been my fav band since I was in 4th grade...im going to respect Heads journey as much as the band does...

~TwEeK~

Hey Cwerky...I just wanted to put this in here to see how long it would take you to figure that that I didnt walk my lazy ass up to the gas station.  You think I would actually walk there...and being drunk...LOL...

Its ok Cwerky...I still love you...

~TwEeK~

Right now I am really fucking drunk...and I have a headache from hell...

I feel really lonely right now too...some times I thing that there is no one out there for me...sometimes I do...but so far no one...I hope I find someone...I am lonely and dont want to be lonely anymore.  I just want someone to love and someone that will love me back...like Yoshi and Cwerky...they love each other...why cant I have what they have.  I guess it just wasnt ment for me.

Alone for the rest of eternity...

~TwEeK~

Every fucking thing is pissing me off right now...mainly the laptop...well thats the only thing that is pissing me off.  It wont let me sign into my e-mail

On another note...today has been really boring...cleaning...again...but its going to end good.  Me and Yoshi went out and got some Sparks...so we will be drunk later on tonight.

The show this weekend is going to be good...especially afterwards...HEHEHE.

I will see you all at the show...hopefully.

~TwEeK~

Yup...so far this day as sucked.  Been cleaning all fucking morning...but it koolwe are getting $60 for doing it.  Well...the rest of my day is probaly free...so give me a call.  If you dont have my cell #...sorry...too fucking bad...

~TwEeK~

What the fuck is wrong with me.  I wish I could figure out why I am the way I am.  Oh well...no one cares anyway...right???

~TwEeK~
